  m_Name: TutorialDialogStatement_02
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  _text: Your new body is frail, and its strength fades. Seek a nearby leyline to
    attune your soul, drawing its potent energies to  siphon its power, fueling your
    essence like a flame devours a candle. Move with caution until the attunement
    is complete.
